name: .liquidmoon | real time
description:
A WebGL real time generative sketch made with GLSL and Threejs, meant to constantly different and impossible to grasp. It changes according to random functions, device, screen resolution and time. Best results with a full screen Chrome browser running.
-
Melting on itself, constructing non-constant identities, incoherent in space and time, establishing itself a dynamic and generative loop between order and chaos, .liquidmoon was inspired by the moon in slithgly cloudy, foggy nights, and represents a constantly changing digital one.
